(788, 313, '_genesis_description', 'With the help of revolutionary treatment REFLEXOLOGY & DORN THERAPY, the world without medicine is the vision and dream of Sajin Antony. For the past 7 years Sajin and his experienced practitioners tirelessly providing healthcare service in Ernakulam District mainly in Varapuzha, Aluva, Perumbavoor. Reflexology is a treatment which has no side effects, particularly for the senior citizen. Sajin has a problem with Varicose Vein while working as an Engineer in Singapore, With the help of  REFLEXOLOGY & DORN THERAPY it has cured. From then onwards Sajin started  REFLEXOLOGY & DORN THERAPY  as a Holistic Treatment. With his wife Nimmy and her sister, Nimmy joined his venture.\r\nWith the help of Church and Clinics Reflexology as given to the world, a being Holistic treatment, and the treatment is free for poor people. '),
