(847, 2, '_panels_data_preview', 'a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:6:{i:0;a:8:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:1555:\"<p>Our team of highly trained professionals uses the latest <strong>healing technologies</strong> to restore you to <strong>pain-free health</strong>, quickly and easily. We thoroughly evaluate &amp; treat all of the contributing root factors related to your issue. This includes, but is not limited to, your work and home stressors, overall<strong> body condition, nutrition, genetic &amp; postural habits, emotional connections and patterns that are held in your muscles</strong></p><h2>Reflexologist Sajin Antony experience</h2><p>With the help of revolutionary treatment <strong><a href=\"http://www.divinesreflexology.com/reflexology/\">REFLEXOLOGY</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://www.divinesreflexology.com/dorn-therapy/\">DORN THERAP</a>Y</strong>, the world without medicine is the vision and dream of Sajin Antony. For the past 7 years Sajin and his experienced practitioners tirelessly providing healthcare service in <strong>Ernakulam District.</strong>Â We have centers mainly in<strong> Varapuzha, Aluva, Perumbavoor</strong>. <strong>Reflexology</strong> is a treatment which has no side effects. Particularly for the senior citizen.</p><p>Sajin has a problem with Varicose Vein while working as an Engineer in Singapore. With the help of <strong>REFLEXOLOGY &amp; <a href=\"http://www.divinesreflexology.com/dorn-therapy/\">DORN </a>THERAPY</strong> it has cured. From then onwards <strong>Sajin</strong> started <strong>REFLEXOLOGY &amp; DORN THERAPY</strong> as a Holistic Treatment. With his wife Nimmy and her sister, Nimmy joined his venture.</p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:4:\"tmce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"587e7159d2a84\";s:14:\"column-classes\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"column-classes-first\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i: